data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 2016 home with over $30k in upgrades conveniently located near Becker Road. 4BD 3BA 3 car garage offers 2500SqFt of living space and the open floor plan makes great for entertaining with an extended bar area and open kitchen. All bedrooms are ample size along with exceptional closet space in primary bedroom. Wood look laminate floors throughout, NO CARPET! Fully Fenced in back yard with large Lanai in the back, and room for a pool. Mature landscaping with an abundance of fruit trees including Mango, Passion Fruit, Banana and many more! Well supplied irrigation has been installed for easy maintenance. 3 minutes from Groceries and shopping, 2 minutes to the Turnpike, 15 minutes or less to Tradition and all shopping needs, 30 minutes to the beach, and 20 minutes to downtown Stuart! This home is move in ready and waiting for you!
